images.description: Designed to suit your needs, the NV Cargo Van is available in Standard and High Roof models, packing a powerful V6 or V8 engine, and backed by a forceful 5-speed automatic transmission - all housed in a rugged, fully boxed frame.
Large sliding doors and low step-ins were purposefully engineered to ensure easy and efficient loading and unloading, so you can get the job done – on time, every time.
Every element of the NV Cargo Van was intelligently designed. A low-sitting bumper, at passenger car height, ensures safer collision compatibility.
The NV High Roof model maximizes your cargo-carrying flexibility with 76.9" of interior height -  you can accommodate a 6'3" person, with room to spare[*] - while 14” Disc Brakes maximize safety.
With a towing capacity of up to 9,500lb, a 5.6-L V8 engine and 317 horsepower, no opportunity is too big to take on.

Choose the drive you need. Both the 24-valve 4.0-L V6 and the 5.6-L V8 deliver seamless power, while specially coated piston skirts and microfinishing help reduce friction for smooth response and less wear and tear.
Transition seamlessly from the office to the road, with more storage space and enough workspace for your laptop.
Customize your interior with 57 total integrated reinforced cargo-mounting points, and maximize floor space with secure exterior roof rack attachment points.

The only available center console in its class transforms the NV Cargo into your mobile office, designed to provide enough space for your laptop and storage for everything from clipboards to hanging files.[*]
Innovative functionality such as a flat loading floor and fork-lift friendly doors that swing 243 degrees wide open, maximize loading capacity so you can handle the big jobs with ease.
Business moves fast, stay connected on the go with the available Technology Package and keep your media at your fingertips with steering wheel-mounted controls.

The key feature of any cargo van is its interior capacity, and the NV Cargo Van offers a spacious 323 cubic feet[*] - roomy enough for two 40" X 48" pallets - so you can transport anything you need, and then some[*].

The NV Passenger Van was engineered for convenience from the ground up. Four rows of seats maximize capacity, while split rear cargo doors allow easy loading and unloading of up to six standard-size suitcases with room to spare.[*]
Sliding doors that open more than 40" and low step-ins make bording a breeze, while moveable seats allow you to tailor your interior to suit your passengers' needs.

The NV Passenger Van features a V6 or V8 engine, plus the largest frame and biggest brakes available in its class, delivering unmatched power and performance, so your passengers have the best ride possible.[*]

Whether you choose the V6 or the V8 engine, you can count on seamless power and and intelligent design. Both run so efficiently so you won't have to worry about logging idling time, while key components reduce friction for smooth response and less wear and tear.
Smooth sliding doors, low step-ins, and side passenger windows outfitted with privacy glass deliver a new level of passenger comfort.

The NV Passenger Van is the only van in its class with standard inflatable curtain air bags for all 4 rows of seats - so you can drive with peace of mind knowing you and your passengers are protected.
Offer first class transportation with seating that features individual backrest design and independent headrests, 12 overhead A/C vents and six individual reading lights.

A class-leading total of six independent rear seats enable you to have unmatched flexibility and up to 10 feet of available cargo space, while dual floor heaters ensure the perfect temperature, every drive.[*]
Dual zone climate control, along with available reading lights and power outlets provide comfort and convenience for both you and your passengers.

An available 12-V power outlet is perfect for charging a cell phone or tablet, while the120-V outlet can power a laptop or other larger electronic device - so you can stay charged and ready for business.

NV Passenger Van’s available center console lets you transition seamlessly from the office to the road, with a workspace large enough for a laptop and storage for everything from clipboards to business cards and even hanging files.
With room for 12 passengers and 324 seat configurations, your cargo capabilities are virtually limitless.[*]
The superior 36.7 foot turning diameter of the NV200 means you're prepared to navigate the most crowded urban spaces and take on the tightest parking spots.

Dual sliding doors provide maximum flexibility when loading and unloading, while a high driver's view point delivers a wider field of vision so you can better negotiate the twists and turns of any environment.
Enjoy a smooth and powerful drive while also keeping your bottom line in check with Best-in-Class[*] 24 city and combined MPG[*] - the first in a family of efficient commercial vehicles.
Keep your business moving with a seat that doubles as a work desk, and a center console that provides enough space for your laptop, file folders and two cup holders.

Steering wheel-mounted controls help you stay in control, while electric power steering automatically adjusts to reduce steering effort at low speeds, so you can focus on what matters when navigating the roads.
